A woman has been remanded in custody after appearing in court charged with giving an 11-month-old boy a bottle feared to contain bleach.

Elaine Joyner, 53, from Deptford, south-east London, appeared at Bromley Magistrates' Court today charged with administering a noxious substance with intent to endanger life, police said.

