Staff in the restaurant raised the alarm and police and paramedics arrived at the branch of McDonald's on Eltham High Street.

Jonjo was taken to hospital with his terrified mum as a search for the suspect was launched.

He was discharged on Thursday night after treatment and is now back home with Samantha and her fiance Ashley Freed.

